Interface Modifiers

All Known Subinterfaces:
IsEmptyPlugin, IsTruePlugin, SqlCountPlugin, SqlExecutionPlugin, SqlFromToPlugin, SqlIdentityPlugin, SqlProcessingIdPlugin, SqlSequencePlugin
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultSqlPlugins
public interface Modifiers
The modifiers are used as the supplement values in the processing of the META SQL statements.
Author:
Vladimir Hudec
